### Call flow and sales force

- Salesforce won't show hold time. But it will show reminders. 

- We may accept the call, we can choose a case to continue working with or create a case

- 7 pieces of information to work with for verification, we need at least 2. 

- Case cannot be open, it might be closed, the only case when it would be needed is for scalations or transfers to sales. 

- Review the call flow guru

-  Case create a case, we may update any typo issue if found. 

- Case clasification is a drop down menu selection and we may memorize an amount of subjects found in Guru. 

- We do not promise calls back, but if call gets disconnected we can call back. 

- Call miner will take the last 2 minutes, important to remember making sure there are no more issues or concerns. 

- 3 mins to make a case. 

- To send emails, we inlcude a hyper link. 
 
